arCallbacks.unk_28bc3c5:
function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idActorGizmo, S_KNOCKBACK_POWER)
	
	-- enable the spawners
	tAllSpawners = Hydra.ActorsInGroup(S_BOSS_ENCOUNTER_SPAWNERS)
	for iter, idSpawner in pairs(tAllSpawners) do
		Hydra.ActorEnable(idSpawner)
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner, false)
	end
	
end

arCallbackSets.unk_98d4504:
-- Kill or Delete all remaining monsters and spawners
tAllSpawnersAndMobs = Hydra.ActorsInGroup(S_BOSS_ENCOUNTER_SPAWNERS)
for iter, idActor in pairs(tAllSpawnersAndMobs) do
	if Hydra.ActorIsMonster(idActor) then
		Hydra.ActorKill(idActor, S_DEATH_OVERRIDE, true, false)
	else
		Hydra.ActorDelete(idActor)
	end
end

Hydra.QuestAdvancePhase()

arQuestPhases.unk_9c63f9d:
-- Destroy Frozen Heart
idHeart = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("DGN_Frac_AnicasClaim_FrozenHeartOfZagraal")[1]
idProxyHeart = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(S_PROXY_ACTOR, idHeart, true, 0, 0)

Hydra.ActorKill(idHeart)

Hydra.Wait(2)

-- Spawn UE as final monster
idFinalMonster = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(S_GOATMEN_UE, 
		idProxyHeart, 
		true, 0,0, 
		Hydra.MR_UNIQUE_ELITE)

Hydra.ActorAddToBossEncounter(idFinalMonster)
